  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_193_000190",
    "sentence": "瀾將被殺，從父弟渤，詣賊救瀾，請代兄死。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_193_000191",
